    Staff --- UC4
    Staff --- UC5
    Staff --- UC6

    UC3 -.->|extends| UC3a
    UC3 -.->|extends| UC3b
    UC3 -.->|extends| UC3c
    UC4 -.->|extends| UC4a
    UC4 -.->|extends| UC4b
    UC4 -.->|extends| UC4c
    UC5 -.->|extends| UC5a
